text: Youm-e-Istehsal (The Day of Exploitation or Kashmir Seize Day) is a Black Day to commemorate the 5th Anniversary 5th day of August, since 2019 of continued Suppression and Illegal Military Occupation and degrading the status of IIOJK and unjust absorption of the Disputed Territory of Indian-Held Jammu & Kashmir government, a direct protest to New Delhi's Presidential Rule. ==Other websites== * Category:Kashmir Category:Holidays of Pakistan Category:August observances
title: Youm-e-Istehsal
